# Exclude domains from generated proxy rules.
# Matching semantics: a listed domain excludes the exact host and all subdomains.
# Inline comments can record the reason an observed host is intentionally excluded.
# Keep entries lowercase and sorted by domain for deterministic rule generation.
app-analytics-services.com # third-party analytics service observed in app captures
myqcloud.com # third-party CDN/license service observed in app captures
